/**
 * PayrollTransactionPostProcessorService
 *
 * Responsibilities:
 *  1) Handle PIM response (single / multi instruction)
 *  2) If top-level post-processing fails AFTER response is received => CANCEL payroll (not SAF/soft)
 *  3) Child-level: update ONLY failed instructions (receiver return code != 0 / error present)
 *  4) Persist ONLY dirty entities (avoid updating everything)
 */
